==English==

===Phrase===
'''[[one]] [[small]] [[step]] [[for]] [[man]], [[one]] [[giant]] [[leap]] [[for]] [[mankind]]'''

# Words spoken by [[w:Neil Armstrong|Neil Armstrong]] when taking the first steps on the [[moon]].
# {{cattag|chiché|idiom}} {{italbrac|used imitatively}} A [[cliché]] used to exaggerate an [[accomplishment]] or [[milestone]].
